    "date": "2021-07-16T18:36:13Z",
    "text": "Superfund Polluter Pays Act\n\nThis bill reinstates and extends the Hazardous Substance Superfund Financing rate through 2025 and increases the rate to 16.3 cents a barrel, adjusted for inflation beginning after 2021.\n\nThe bill imposes on corporations a 0.12% tax of the excess of the modified environmental tax taxable income of the corporation over $3.13 million."
